products.title: Intel Core i7-7700 Desktop Processor 4 Cores up to 4.2 GHz LGA 1151 100/200 Series 65W
features: 3.60 GHz up to 4.20 GHz Max Turbo Frequency / 8 MB Cache

products.description: Are you amazed by the things you can do with your computer? . If you bought your computer more than a handful of years ago, you're missing more than you know - uncompromised gaming, while you stream, chat and share with your community - stunning visuals of 4K HDR premium content - transport into a great VR experience. With premium performance and new & enhanced features, a desktop computer based on an 7th Gen Intel Core processor is always ready for real-life productivity, creativity and entertainment. With a range of smart, stylish designs and sizes, there is a 7th Gen Intel Core Desktop powered computer to fit a wide range of budgets and needs.
